        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[【[吃惊]#眼睛干涩也可能是颈椎有问题#】颈椎“完蛋”的表现，能有成千上百种，还都看起来没啥关联！比如头晕、头疼、眼睛干涩、耳石症等，都可能和颈椎退化相关...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[吃惊]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chijing-59b444adb6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%9C%BC%E7%9D%9B%E5%B9%B2%E6%B6%A9%E4%B9%9F%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E9%A2%88%E6%A4%8E%E6%9C%89%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%9C%BC%E7%9D%9B%E5%B9%B2%E6%B6%A9%E4%B9%9F%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E9%A2%88%E6%A4%8E%E6%9C%89%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#眼睛干涩也可能是颈椎有问题#</span></a>】颈椎“完蛋”的表现，能有成千上百种，还都看起来没啥关联！比如头晕、头疼、眼睛干涩、耳石症等，都可能和颈椎退化相关，还越来越低龄化<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[允悲]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_yunbei-a14a649db8.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%AE%80%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%86%E8%A6%81%E5%9D%9A%E6%8C%81%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%89%E4%BC%B8%E5%8A%A8%E4%BD%9C%E6%94%BE%E6%9D%BE%E9%A2%88%E6%A4%8E%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%AE%80%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%86%E8%A6%81%E5%9D%9A%E6%8C%81%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%89%E4%BC%B8%E5%8A%A8%E4%BD%9C%E6%94%BE%E6%9D%BE%E9%A2%88%E6%A4%8E%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#简单但要坚持的拉伸动作放松颈椎#</span></a> 和卫一起试试吧！<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[收到]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/8b/2022_get_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>（央视新闻） <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4976674089926688" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hkmc8wh67fj61hc0u07gt02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><sou