            <title><![CDATA[天气凉爽，温度正好，可在家久坐竟会感觉手冰脚凉[揣手]和小卫一起整一套“臀桥”动作吧，不仅能有效锻炼肌肉力量，还能改善骨盆与腰椎的稳定度[doge]👇🏻#...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[天气凉爽，温度正好，可在家久坐竟会感觉手冰脚凉<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[揣手]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/af/2022_chuaishou_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>和小卫一起整一套“臀桥”动作吧，不仅能有效锻炼肌肉力量，还能改善骨盆与腰椎的稳定度<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视一套）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4779963182940212" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视一套的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/78ad4dbbly1h36sbkln13j20ru0fo764.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/p4hgfhnTlx07WOHJX3DG01041200hcbh0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1702098922&amp;ssig=QFVz8paMrf&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/dzCMIH5ulx07WOHJ1erC010412007LeG0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1702098922&amp;ssig=ipQ5oU6abE&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/inut55Wjlx07WOHJmilq0104120059e70E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1702098922&amp;ssig=wZbZL2GndP&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4779963182940212" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
